ng\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2x+1=10<br />\n2x=9<br />\nx=4.5<br />\n<br />\n利伸 phd in mathematics (harvard)"},{"pid":"fc4206f96784974fb21ea6bead4f1e52992f7862","tid":40890,"uid":20535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"給定一個任意正整數，如果該數是2的倍數，將其除2，如果不是2的倍數，將其乘3再加一。證明不停重複上述步驟，在有限次數下會得到1。"}]}